<span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span> Having once been employed by a leading multinational, Miles Kubheka went out on a limb and ingeniously created a restaurant with the same name and branding as a fictional restaurant portrayed in a famous ‘big dreamer’ TV ad campaign. In doing so, he catapulted into media stardom, and soon translated his innovative thinking into entrepreneurial success. Driven by tenacity, optimism and self-belief, Kubheka is uniquely capable of inspiring audiences to dream big but execute with practicality. Brought to you by Nedbank Private Wealth.